  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - Now we can begin the Moonheart Elixir itself. This is the final Moonwarden recipe.
  - Its purpose is to reconnect what has been weakened.
  - The order matters. Balance must be built slowly, one piece at a time.
  - The meadow has been waiting for someone willing to listen to it.
  - Now... brew the elixir.
  - Remember the sequence carefully.
  - Each step is as important as the last one.
  - You did it... The Elixir is finally ready...
